---
title: Parmesan Chicken Schnitzels with Pear Salad & Truffle Mayo
description: It's easy to whip up a classic schnitzel at home, and we're going to show you how! Then, make it a meal with a sweet and crisp
salad, studded with pear, plus some truffle mayo for dipping. Delicious!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
